---
title: Warming Veggie 'Nduja, Chorizo and Sweet Potato Rice Bowl with Black Beans, Spinach and Flaked Almonds
description: This Warming Veggie 'Nduja, Chorizo and Sweet Potato Rice Bowl will be on your table in less than 25 minutes. Featuring a hot, umami blend of Calabrian chillies and peppers, this 'Nduja is completely meat-free but with all the same flavour.
